        <mxCell id="p3_desc" value="&amp;bull; Scaffold Django 5 project (5 apps), DRF, SimpleJWT, PostgreSQL+pgvector&lt;br&gt;&amp;bull; Build 15+ REST endpoints: auth, training CRUD, quiz grading, compliance, incidents&lt;br&gt;&amp;bull; Build React 18 + Vite SPA: 6 screens, JWT interceptor, sidebar navigation&lt;br&gt;&amp;bull; RAG chatbot: fastembed → pgvector L2Distance → OpenRouter Llama 4 Maverick&lt;br&gt;&amp;bull; Seed database: 3 modules, 3 requirements, 5 knowledge-base documents" style="text;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=11;fontColor=#cffafe;" vertex="1" parent="1">
