        <mxCell id="p4_desc" value="&amp;bull; Unit testing: Django test cases for all API endpoints&lt;br&gt;&amp;bull; Integration testing: React ↔ Django ↔ PostgreSQL data-flow validation&lt;br&gt;&amp;bull; Security: JWT expiry, role-based route protection, CORS, SQL injection&lt;br&gt;&amp;bull; RAG accuracy: top-5 relevance scoring on 10 sample questions&lt;br&gt;&amp;bull; UAT: walk through all 10 business metrics; cross-browser testing" style="text;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=11;fontColor=#fef3c7;" vertex="1" parent="1">
