        <mxCell id="p5_desc" value="&amp;bull; Deploy Django to Render: Gunicorn, env vars, auto-migrate, seed_data&lt;br&gt;&amp;bull; Deploy React to Vercel: VITE_API_URL, SPA rewrite rules, auto-deploy on push&lt;br&gt;&amp;bull; Provision Supabase PostgreSQL: pgvector extension, transaction-pooling&lt;br&gt;&amp;bull; Configure OpenRouter API key + run ingest_docs on production instance&lt;br&gt;&amp;bull; Cold-start UX: frontend warm-up request → retry; smoke test on production" style="text;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=11;fontColor=#fee2e2;" vertex="1" parent="1">
