        <mxCell id="p6_desc" value="&amp;bull; Monitor Render runtime logs &amp; Supabase performance metrics&lt;br&gt;&amp;bull; Bug fixes &amp; dependency security updates (Django, React, Axios)&lt;br&gt;&amp;bull; RAG tuning: chunk size/overlap optimisation, prompt template iteration&lt;br&gt;&amp;bull; Track HIPAA/GDPR regulatory changes → update knowledge-base docs&lt;br&gt;&amp;bull; Periodic audits: user access reviews, API security scans, data integrity" style="text;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=11;fontColor=#d1fae5;" vertex="1" parent="1">
